KORISNI LINKOVI:
# http://guides.rubygems.org/make-your-own-gem/
# http://railsconftutorials.com/2013/sessions/crafting_gems.html

STRUKTURA RUBY GEM
------------------

FOLDER:
* LIB = Ruby code related to library
* PKG = Temp dir, gem is generated here
* TEST = unit test, scripts...
* DOC = Optional, documentation
* BIN = Optional, system tools, cli scripts
* ROOT = gemspec, 

FILES:
* naziv_gema.gemspec


CREATE GEM:
* gem build <spec_file> # string_extend.gemspec
